Ley Line Rifter
A sorcerer who has mastered opening, closing, and traversing dimensional
Rifts, walking the most dangerous path of all magic users.

Skill categories: Technical, Science, Lore, Physical.
Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 14.
Starting equipment: Traveller's robes, dimensional compass, ley line map
fragments, spellbook, arcane focus, and concealed sidearm. Magic OCC (PPE).
